PRECISION Air will launch the direct flights to Dodoma from Dar es Salaam effective April this year. Precision Air Marketing and Corporate Affairs Manager, Hillary Mremi said in a statement issued in Dar es Salaam yesterday that the new route will also include flights between Kilimanjaro and Dodoma. “We will operate six flights a week, every Monday, Tuesday, Wednesday, Thursday, Friday and Saturday. On Wednesday and Friday the flight will operate via Kilimanjaro while the rest of the days it will be a direct flight,” he said. He added, “Our new flight will connect Dodoma with Mtwara, Dar es Salaam, Mwanza, Arusha and Nairobi via Dar es Salaam and Kilimanjaro. Passengers from these destinations can easily connect to Dodoma with our flights, and we are proud to accomplish the mission of connecting communities,” According to the statement, the direct flight to Dodoma will be departing Dar es Salaam at 09:15am and arrive in Dodoma at 10:20am, while the flight which goes via Kilimanjaro will be departing at 2:00pm and arrive in Dodoma at 16:50pm.